@startuml srs-change-sequence
!theme plain
title Sequence: SRS Change Detected

actor "GitHub" as Git
participant "Webhook" as Hook
participant "Parser" as Parser
participant "Classifier" as Class
participant "Resolver" as Res
participant "Document\nOwner" as Owner
participant "Jira" as Jira

Git -> Hook: POST new commit
Hook -> Parser: parse SRS diff
Parser -> Class: classify change\ntype (Risk/UI/etc)
Class -> Res: resolve impacted docs
Res -> Owner: send findings
Owner -> Jira: acknowledge
note over Owner, Jira: Owner reviews\nusing traceability tables

@enduml